---
import Card from "./Card/index.astro";
import { Icon } from 'astro-icon/components';
---

<Card colSpan="md:col-span-3" rowSpan="md:row-span-2" variant="gradient">
  <div class="flex w-full h-full">
    <div class="flex flex-col justify-between md:max-w-[700px] gap-3 sm:gap-5">
      <div class="flex flex-col gap-2 sm:gap-3">
        <h1 class="text-lg sm:text-xl font-bold flex items-center">
          <div class="tech-icon-container">
            <Icon name="ri:user-3-fill" class="h-6 w-6 sm:h-7 sm:w-7 text-red-500" />
          </div>
          <span class="text-gradient ml-2">My Background</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="text-sm sm:text-base leading-relaxed text-gray-100">
          I graduated with a degree in Software Engineering from Polytechnic, which provided me with a strong technical foundation. My passion for continuous learning led me to obtain specialized certifications in RedHat technologies, Python programming, Data Science, and most recently AI development.
        </p>
        <p class="text-sm sm:text-base leading-relaxed text-gray-100 mt-2">
          My professional journey began in 2010 as a journalist and marketing specialist, which helped me develop strong communication skills. I later transitioned to digital marketing, leveraging my technical background to bring a unique perspective to SEO strategies. Since 2021, I've been exploring AI technologies from prompt engineering to model training, which I now integrate into my marketing approaches. In recent years, I founded SingRank, where I apply my diverse skill set to help businesses in Singapore and internationally.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h3 class="text-sm sm:text-base font-semibold mb-3 sm:mb-4 flex items-center">
          <div class="tech-icon-container">
            <Icon name="ri:tools-fill" class="h-5 w-5 sm:h-6 sm:w-6 text-red-500" />
          </div>
          <span class="text-gradient ml-2">Personal Skills & Expertise</span>
        </h3>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-3 sm:gap-4">
          <div class="tech-skill-group">
            <h4 class="text-xs sm:text-sm font-medium mb-3 text-white/90 tech-group-title">Digital Marketing</h4>
            <ul class="space-y-2">
              <li class="flex items-center text-xs sm:text-sm">
                <div class="tech-skill-icon">
                  <Icon name="ri:search-eye-fill" class="h-4 w-4 sm:h-5 sm:w-5 text-red-500" />
                </div>
                <span>SEO & AEO Strategy</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-center text-xs sm:text-sm">
                <div class="tech-skill-icon">
                  <Icon name="ri:line-chart-fill" class="h-4 w-4 sm:h-5 sm:w-5 text-red-500" />
                </div>
                <span>Digital Marketing Consulting</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-center text-xs sm:text-sm">
                <div class="tech-skill-icon">
                  <Icon name="ri:building-4-fill" class="h-4 w-4 sm:h-5 sm:w-5 text-red-500" />
                </div>
                <span>Business Leadership</span>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          
          <div class="tech-skill-group">
            <h4 class="text-xs sm:text-sm font-medium mb-3 text-white/90 tech-group-title">AI & Technology</h4>
            <ul class="space-y-2">
              <li class="flex items-center text-xs sm:text-sm">
                <div class="tech-skill-icon">
                  <Icon name="ri:brain-fill" class="h-4 w-4 sm:h-5 sm:w-5 text-red-500" />
                </div>
                <span>AI Prompt Engineering</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-center text-xs sm:text-sm">
                <div class="tech-skill-icon">
                  <Icon name="ri:code-s-slash-fill" class="h-4 w-4 sm:h-5 sm:w-5 text-red-500" />
                </div>
                <span>Model Training & Deployment</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-center text-xs sm:text-sm">
                <div class="tech-skill-icon">
                  <Icon name="ri:code-box-fill" class="h-4 w-4 sm:h-5 sm:w-5 text-red-500" />
                </div>
                <span>Python & Data Science</span>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          
          <div class="tech-skill-group">
            <h4 class="text-xs sm:text-sm font-medium mb-3 text-white/90 tech-group-title">Education & Certifications</h4>
            <ul class="space-y-2">
              <li class="flex items-center text-xs sm:text-sm">
                <div class="tech-skill-icon">
                  <Icon name="ri:graduation-cap-fill" class="h-4 w-4 sm:h-5 sm:w-5 text-red-500" />
                </div>
                <span>Software Engineering Degree</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-center text-xs sm:text-sm">
                <div class="tech-skill-icon">
                  <Icon name="ri:medal-fill" class="h-4 w-4 sm:h-5 sm:w-5 text-red-500" />
                </div>
                <span>RedHat Certification</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-center text-xs sm:text-sm">
                <div class="tech-skill-icon">
                  <Icon name="ri:award-fill" class="h-4 w-4 sm:h-5 sm:w-5 text-red-500" />
                </div>
                <span>Data Science & AI Training</span>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          
          <div class="tech-skill-group">
            <h4 class="text-xs sm:text-sm font-medium mb-3 text-white/90 tech-group-title">Communication & Strategy</h4>
            <ul class="space-y-2">
              <li class="flex items-center text-xs sm:text-sm">
                <div class="tech-skill-icon">
                  <Icon name="ri:article-fill" class="h-4 w-4 sm:h-5 sm:w-5 text-red-500" />
                </div>
                <span>Journalism & Content Creation</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-center text-xs sm:text-sm">
                <div class="tech-skill-icon">
                  <Icon name="ri:global-fill" class="h-4 w-4 sm:h-5 sm:w-5 text-red-500" />
                </div>
                <span>International Business</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-center text-xs sm:text-sm">
                <div class="tech-skill-icon">
                  <Icon name="ri:lightbulb-fill" class="h-4 w-4 sm:h-5 sm:w-5 text-red-500" />
                </div>
                <span>Strategic Problem Solving</span>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Card>

<style>
.tech-skill-group {
  padding: 1rem;
  border-radius: 0.5rem;
  background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);
  border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
  border-left: 2px solid rgba(229, 62, 62, 0.4);
  box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
  backdrop-filter: blur(4px);
  position: relative;
  overflow: hidden;
}

.tech-skill-group::after {
  content: "";
  position: absolute;
  top: 0;
  left: 0;
  width: 100%;
  height: 1px;
  background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, rgba(229, 62, 62, 0.3), transparent);
}

.tech-group-title {
  position: relative;
  display: inline-block;
  padding-bottom: 0.5rem;
}

.tech-group-title::after {
  content: "";
  position: absolute;
  bottom: 0;
  left: 0;
  width: 40%;
  height: 1px;
  background-color: rgba(229, 62, 62, 0.5);
}

.tech-skill-icon {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  width: 32px;
  height: 32px;
  background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
  border: 1px solid rgba(229, 62, 62, 0.2);
  border-radius: 6px;
  margin-right: 10px;
  box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
}

.tech-icon-container {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  width: 40px;
  height: 40px;
  background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
  border: 1px solid rgba(229, 62, 62, 0.3);
  border-radius: 10px;
  position: relative;
  overflow: hidden;
}

.tech-icon-container::before {
  content: "";
  position: absolute;
  top: 0;
  left: 0;
  width: 100%;
  height: 100%;
  background: linear-gradient(45deg, transparent, rgba(229, 62, 62, 0.1), transparent);
  animation: shine 3s infinite;
}

@keyframes shine {
  0% {
    transform: translateX(-100%) translateY(-100%);
  }
  50% {
    transform: translateX(100%) translateY(100%);
  }
  100% {
    transform: translateX(100%) translateY(100%);
    opacity: 0;
  }
}
</style>
